:"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">LunarShaddow</span> 说: 嘛，反正Fedora和Ubuntu是全自动的……<br>这功能起因是好的，防止Win/Linux内核被人偷换/插入恶意组件，所以要求签名；<br>但是M$把持了笔电厂商，笔电厂商锁掉了主板添加公钥的功能，里面只有...</q></div>在我看來，「微软不愿意签任何GPLv3的东西」已經讓「这功能起因是好的」缺乏說服力了…… 畢竟 M$。如果微軟只在「小白機」上 Secure Boot 也就算了，看它當初的架勢是想普及 Secure Boot，沒想給 Linux 留一畝三分地啊……"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/82/208208.jpg","floor":"#2-12","id":"1240740","time":"2017-5-24 14:33","userId":"aflyhorse","userName":"LunarShaddow🌙","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Franklin Yu</span> 说: 在我看來，「微软不愿意签任何GPLv3的东西」已經讓「这功能起因是好的」缺乏說服力了…… 畢竟 M$。如果微軟只在「小白機」上 Secure Boot 也就算了，看它當初的架勢是想普及 Secure ...</q></div>嘛……现在安卓机花样繁多的bootloader lock（大陆简称BL锁）不也是类似的东西嘛……"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/78/177820.jpg","floor":"#2-13","id":"1241116","time":"2017-5-25 01:46","userId":"franklinyu","userName":"Franklin Yu","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">LunarShaddow</span> 说: 嘛……现在安卓机花样繁多的bootloader lock（大陆简称BL锁）不也是类似的东西嘛……</q></div>不懂安卓，那個是刷機的時候會涉及的？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/82/208208.jpg","floor":"#2-14","id":"1241411","time":"2017-5-25 23:31","userId":"aflyhorse","userName":"LunarShaddow🌙","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Franklin Yu</span> 说: 不懂安卓，那個是刷機的時候會涉及的？</q></div>是的；勉强可以理解为initrd"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/78/177820.jpg","floor":"#2-15","id":"1241433","time":"2017-5-26 00:52","userId":"franklinyu","userName":"Franklin Yu","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">LunarShaddow</span> 说: 是的；勉强可以理解为initrd</q></div>那確實很 dirty…… 不過國內公司就這尿性，巨硬作為美帝巨頭，不應該跟他們同流合汙的……"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/61/36176.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1240371","time":"2017-5-23 23:31","userId":"36176","userName":"豆沙包罐头","userSign":"(事到如今数不完了呀)","message":"还没被坑够吗","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/p